<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .header {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .header strong {
      font-size: 18px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .content {
      color: #333333;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }
    .event-details {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 15px 0;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .event-details p {
      margin: 5px 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #333333;
    }
    .link {
      color: #0066cc;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 25px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888888;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #0066cc;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @vendor_contact.business_name.present? ? @vendor_contact.business_name.split(' ').first : @vendor_contact.name.split(' ').first %>,</p>

      <p>We're pumped to announce that submissions are officially open for the next <strong><%= @event.title %></strong><% if @event.venue.present? %> at <strong><%= @event.venue %></strong><% end %><% if @event.event_date.present? %> on <strong><%= @event.event_date.strftime("%A, %B %-d, %Y") %></strong><% end %>.</p>

      <p>Submit your work below:</p>

      <%
        # Get vendor application links
        app_links = @invitation.vendor_application_links
        artist_link = app_links.find { |link| link[:name].downcase.include?('artist') }
        vendor_link = app_links.find { |link| link[:name].downcase.include?('vendor') }
      %>

      <% if artist_link %>
        <p><strong>ARTIST / GALLERY SUBMISSIONS</strong><br/>
        For artists exhibiting artwork on the walls<br/>
        <a href="<%= artist_link[:url] %>" class="link">Apply Here</a></p>
      <% end %>

      <% if vendor_link %>
        <p><strong>TABLE VENDOR SUBMISSIONS</strong><br/>
        For those setting up a TABLE space (Clothing, jewelry, and other table merch)<br/>
        <a href="<%= vendor_link[:url] %>" class="link">Apply Here</a></p>
      <% end %>

      <p>I'm looking forward to your submission.</p>

      <p>Thanks,<br/><%= @organization.name %></p>

      <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px;">P.S. If you can't make the date, please <a href="<%= @unsubscribe_url %>" class="link">let us know here</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 12px; color: #888888;">
        Questions? Reply to this email or contact team@voxxypresents.com directly.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #aaaaaa;">Powered by Voxxy Presents</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
